The event is centered around two elaborate Civil War battle reenactments complete with authentic cannons, troop camps, and sutlers' tents.
Other events include a picnic basket auction, the Miss Confederacy pageant, and a grand ball.
The 90-year-old celebration is documented in text and photographs.
